@SmartArchivistApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:8081
@documentId = replace-with-actual-id

### Get all documents
GET {{SmartArchivistApi_HostAddress}}/api/documents
Accept: application/json

###

### Upload document
POST {{SmartArchivistApi_HostAddress}}/api/documents/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Name"

Test Document
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="File"; filename="test.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/test.pdf
--boundary--

###

### Get all documents
GET {{SmartArchivistApi_HostAddress}}/api/documents
Accept: application/json

###

### Get document by ID
GET {{SmartArchivistApi_HostAddress}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Download document
GET {{SmartArchivistApi_HostAddress}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/download     

###

### Search documents
GET {{SmartArchivistApi_HostAddress}}/api/documents/search?query=test
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete document
DELETE {{SmartArchivistApi_HostAddress}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}